com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.matrix.v1

Class MatrixParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.marcoshsc.orsApiTools.matrix.v1.MatrixParameters
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParameterList

    public class MatrixParameters
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParameterList
    Set of query parameters used in requests to the ORS API, in the matrix path. Implements ParameterList, which means there is a method called getUsedParameters(), that returns the not null fields on the object. By default, all the fields are null. The user must make it's own configuration.
    Author:
    Marcos Henrique Santos Cunha in 21-03-2020

      • destinations

        private Destinations destinations
        A comma separated list of indices that refers to the list of locations.

      • metrics

        private Metrics metrics
        Specifies a list of returned metrics separated with a pipe character (|). distance - Returns distance matrix for specified points in defined units. duration - Returns duration matrix for specified points in seconds.

      • resolveLocations

        private ResolveLocations resolveLocations
        Specifies whether given locations are resolved or not. If the parameter value set to true, every element in destinations and sources will contain the name element that identifies the name of the closest street. Default: false

      • optimized

        private Optimized optimized
        Specifies whether Dijkstra algorithm (false) or any available technique to speed up shortest-path routing (true) is used. For normal Dijkstra the number of visited nodes is limited to 100000

      • units

        private Units units
        Specifies the unit of measurement for distances (only).

      • id

        private Id id
        Arbitrary identification string of the request reflected in the meta information.
